Social Auth Facebook requires Facebook PHP Library. Make sure the library is installed via Composer.
Social Auth Google requires Google_Client PHP Library. Make sure the library is installed via Composer.
Social Auth LinkedIn requires LinkedIn PHP Library. Make sure the library is installed via Composer.
Social Auth Twitter requires TwitterOAuth PHP Library. Make sure the library is installed via Composer.
